{"tid":1908184,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本專家：年輕人易播毒，避開人群，就是拯救生命","createTime":"2020-03-03T05:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T16:22:39.000Z","uid":212626,"like":25,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ce023e7a240a1c56d3b0c31b6f7a6d49e1898e36","tid":1908184,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:56:43.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎）在全球多國蔓延，新冠肺炎症狀因人而異，有確診患者沒有病徵。<span style=\"color: red;\">日本專家擔心，年輕人感染新冠肺炎後病徵較輕微，容易在無意中傳播病毒擴大疫情。日本專家坦言，年輕人避開人群，就是拯救生命</span>。<br />\n<br />\n共同社報道，日本政府專家周一（2日）召開會議，指出年輕人感染新冠肺炎的重症化風險低，而輕症患者在沒有意識情況下，對新冠疫情擴散發揮重要作用。<br />\n<br />\n專家呼籲日本全國10至39歲年輕人：光是避開人群聚集、通風差的場所，就能拯救生命。<br />\n<br />\n北海道是日本疫情最嚴重地區，確診人數超過70。專家會議更料，北海道截至2月25日，實際已有940名新冠肺炎患者，只是很多都是未被發現的輕症患者。<br />\n<br />\n專家分析認為，北海道確診患者分佈廣泛，是因為年輕人活躍活動，在高風險場所染病後，將病毒帶到北海道內遠處傳染老年人。<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2579711/</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6w4y0e3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6w4y0e3.gif&h=4ffa330e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b8fb8c72cd87d69b88c7a170d09e0380d919ded","tid":1908184,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6dd199b86451abb1a582ef5306d788d882a09e","tid":1908184,"uid":212626,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:58:48.000Z","msg":"專家食屎.jpg"},{"pid":"4bd28cf610e4c78f5f387021d5fc97af48d2ba2e","tid":1908184,"uid":294614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n[1118 理大營救戰] 有冇人仲記得人踩人前發生左咩事 --油麻地消防局/救護車站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1908167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1908167</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55f0ffc2d3db3166b5e449c8f5ec89f2ef62f62","tid":1908184,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bbd177120ab866ace985661360a584c79dd895","tid":1908184,"uid":14918,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uty4nvu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUty4nvu.jpg&h=052c95a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85b199027bf81892e32fc230e8ca3831592a5abb","tid":1908184,"uid":76933,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"BR法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6711bc99fc2d59c9ef7980b35f22d6a50d2c36b6","tid":1908184,"uid":348849,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"遠離人群<br />\n遠離車群<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f942352ded717cb82053c845541c8c24ea979ae","tid":1908184,"uid":322732,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"係咪講溜左老人中年鐘意聚會宴會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240c935831402f9e9cf510d88723b4aa224e0463","tid":1908184,"uid":93752,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:05:36.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歧視年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce559723d70876ed76bc6fa69de4f1ea3921da06","tid":1908184,"uid":288670,"like":3,"disli