:"咁都有得賴<br />\n不如話廢老加強抵抗力，叫少d雞，咪無咁易染病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd07206d9ead0c1492b2c9adcf63d427b61281d9","tid":1908184,"uid":46947,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYNXHxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYNXHxx.jpg&h=149e36f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b99192732e5836dfdd96bc048382fcd50386409","tid":1908184,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:09:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"56c90ba66c9144af9d5a97b43355828552b7caf6","tid":1908184,"uid":289708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"年輕人是原罪"},{"pid":"7f9d9020ca7046f5e7d882f16538b47a087430bb","tid":1908184,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"香港老細: 記得準時返工"},{"pid":"6beab56dfb4e354329b01ca6fb0f36b6f64cd778","tid":1908184,"uid":288670,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"仆街經濟日報已經係同大公 文匯同級紅報 依家連登紅毛/狗好鍾意拎經濟日報帶風向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《香港經濟日報》是香港的財經報章，於1988年創辦。她是香港主要財經報章，其內容以中產及專業人士為導向，和《信報》同一為「嚴肅報章」。該報於2011年7月出版免費報章《晴報》。<br />\n<br />\n《香港經濟日報》被網民指斥內容親建制及親中。經濟日報集團主席<br />\n馮紹波<br />\n有深厚親中背景，屬七十年代港大國粹派骨幹，在董建華任特首時開始獲特區政府器重。馮在董、曾兩朝公職未算突出，暗地經營政治力量；梁振英競選特首時，馮亦被視為「暗盤梁粉」，邵善波更是其老朋友"},{"pid":"ea88c6238a87a7306d34a8bdeea457b87c61789b","tid":1908184,"uid":22869,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8702f2a32d961c8570b07fda8a313372b5064c84","tid":1908184,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/03/a527e8bad797--.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftchina.kyodonews.net%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2Fa527e8bad797--.html&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVprtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=e3fc34ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tchina.kyodonews.net/news/2020/03/a527e8bad797--.html</a>"},{"pid":"cf9813d71ca648457644f853e3f9f39303248fdf","tid":1908184,"uid":55568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:16:42.000Z","msg":"即係多去聚會就可以除老害<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bf6696ae11272a6f75ba85bf30a2e3d428599c","tid":1908184,"uid":288670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"日本共產黨的《赤旗》是極左，有壹定的社會影響力。共同社是通訊社，負責配發新聞，牠不是新聞社。在戰前是極左，現在仍比《朝日新聞》要左，當然通訊社在思想性方麵是和報社沒法比的，就像新華社不可能超過《人民日報》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.creaders.net/politics/bbsviewer.php?trd_id=709084&amp;language=big5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.creaders.net%2Fpolitics%2Fbbsviewer.php%3Ftrd_id%3D709084%26language%3Dbig5&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVprtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=27635a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.creaders.net/politics/bbsviewer.php?trd_id=709084&amp;language=big5</a>"},{"pid":"692557cc0d77c05ced43c2573fc4a8cd9e1095a4","tid":1908184,"uid":213747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6beab56dfb4e354329b01ca6fb0f36b6f64cd778","tid":1908184,"uid":288670,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:10:45.000Z","msg":"仆街經濟日報已經係同大公 文匯同級紅報 依家連登紅毛/狗好鍾意拎經濟日報帶風向<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《香港經濟日報》是香港的財經報章，於1988年創辦。她是香港主要財經報章，其內容以中產及專業人士為導向，和《信報》同一為「嚴肅報章」。該報於2011年7月出版免費報章《晴報》。<br />\n<br />\n《香港經濟日報》被網民指斥內容親建制及親中。經濟日報集團主席<br />\n馮紹波<br />\n有深厚親中背景，屬七十年代港大國粹派骨幹，在董建華任特首時開始獲特區政府器重。馮在董、曾兩朝公職未算突出，暗地經營政治力量；梁振英競選特首時，馮亦被視為「暗盤梁粉」，邵善波更是其老朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"經濟日報只係引述<br />\n琴日全日「若者のせい」都長霸日本twitter trend第一位<br />\n<br />\n不過唔好淨係話年輕人<br />\n成個日本喺武漢肺炎嘅反應上都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"cd07206d9ead0c1492b2c9adcf63d427b61281d9","tid":1908184,"uid":46947,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bYNXHxx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbYNXHxx.jpg&h=149e36f6&s={SIZE}\" />"}}